cardList.title: Lil Uzi Vert Eternal Atake Sweatpants
cardList.desc: The Eternal Atake sweatpants feature the text Eternal Atake running down the right leg, the number 27 on the right leg and two symbols on the top.  All designs are in glitter shimmer crystalina on white 100% cotton, unisex Los Angeles Apparel sweatpants made in the USA. This bundle also includes a digital download of Lil Uzi Vert's album Eternal Atake Deluxe

cardList.title: adidas YEEZY BOOST 700 MNVN Phosphor
cardList.desc: The upper of the latest YEEZY sneaker features a padded upper constructed of durable neon yellow nylon, dressed with an array of heat-welded reflective 3M “700” overlays on the lateral sides. Contrasting hits of black are also found around the toe, heel, tongue and collar regions. Elevating the shoe is a black BOOST-assisted midsole paired with matching rubber outsole.
